OL,7,FAn "obsessed" former police constable
OL,8,Fconvicted of stalking his estranged
OL,9,Fpolicewoman wife who he caught having
OL,10,Fsex with a colleague has walked free
OL,11,Ffrom court.
OL,13,FGavin Harper, 45, discovered the
OL,14,Flovers in a Screwfix car park in
OL,15,FBirkenhead, Merseyside, after he
OL,16,Fsecretly placed a tracker device on
OL,17,Fthe underside of Stephanie Glynn's
OL,18,Fvehicle.
