OL,7,FMerseyside Police officers Ms Glynn,
OL,8,F40, and Inspector Andrew McLullich,
OL,9,F42, were naked from the waist down in
OL,10,Fthe back of the latter's car when
OL,11,FHarper crept up and filmed them at the
OL,12,Fwindow with his mobile phone.
OL,14,FProsecutors said it was the
OL,15,Fculmination of a campaign of
OL,16,F"obsessive, intrusive and unwanted
OL,17,Fbehaviour" against Ms Glynn from
OL,18,FDecember 2020 to February 2021,
