OL,7,FLast month a jury at Liverpool Crown
OL,8,FCourt found the father-of-two guilty
OL,9,Fof aggravated stalking which included
OL,10,Fsecretly bugging Ms Glynn's car,
OL,11,Flistening to her conservations,
OL,12,Ftracking her whereabouts and taking
OL,13,Fher phone without her permission.
OL,15,FThe defendant and Ms Glynn met as
OL,16,FMerseyside Police officers and were in
OL,17,Fa six-year relationship before they
OL,18,Fmarried in 2018.
