OL,7,FBut Ms Glynn left the family home in
OL,8,FDecember 2020 after she grew close to
OL,9,Fher work mentor Mr McLullich, an
OL,10,Facting inspector at the time and
OL,11,Fformerly her supervising sergeant.
OL,13,FGiving evidence, Harper said he wanted
OL,14,F"undeniable proof" of the affair which
OL,15,Fhe said Ms Glynn had persistently
OL,16,Fdenied.
