OL,7,FHis intention was to pass the video to
OL,8,Fpolice as evidence of two serving
OL,9,Fofficers having an inappropriate
OL,10,Frelationship during Covid lockdown
OL,11,Frestrictions, he said.
OL,13,FOn Monday, Judge David Potter
OL,14,Fsentenced Harper to two years in jail,
OL,15,Fsuspended for two years.
OL,17,FThe judge told him he would have faced
OL,18,Fimmediate custody but for the
OL,19,Fsignificant effect that imprisonment
OL,20,Fwould have had on Harper's elderly
OL,21,Fparents and youngest son.
