OL,7,FHis barrister told the court that
OL,8,FHarper would lose his security job if
OL,9,Fjailed and would be unable to make his
OL,10,Fmortgage payments. His parents, who he
OL,11,Finformally cared for, would "not be
OL,12,Fable to cope" and his son would have
