OL,7,FHe said the events at Screwfix "do no
OL,8,Fcredit to any of the people involved"
OL,9,Fand the incident was "rash, foolish,
OL,10,Fselfish and unprofessional".
OL,12,FJudge Potter went on: "I am sure it
OL,13,Fhas haunted them (Ms Glynn and Mr
OL,14,FMcLullich) and will continue to haunt
OL,15,Fthem for many years."
OL,17,FBut he said their acts were "made
OL,18,Fworse" by Harper filming them on his
OL,19,Fmobile phone.
