OL,7,FThe judge issued Harper with seven-
OL,8,Fyear restraining orders from
OL,9,Fcontacting or approaching Ms Glynn and
OL,10,FMr McLullich.
OL,12,FHarper must also perform 200 hours of
OL,13,Funpaid work and complete 20 days of
OL,14,Frehabilitation.
OL,16,FThe Crown offered no evidence over an
OL,17,Fallegation that Harper unlawfully
OL,18,Fwounded Mr McLullich in the Screwfix
OL,19,Fcar park after jurors could not reach
OL,20,Fa verdict on that charge.
